reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made with a soft, warm fabric that's not itchy, and appreciate its perfect weight for winter wear. Customers like the fit, with one noting the ribbing around the wrists hugs nicely, and the v-neck collar design adds to its classy appearance.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice fit
items.body: Spot on size. Nice and long, beautiful color. Great quality. Cozy, beautiful, stylish.. Read more
items.author: Pamela Taylor-Horton

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars I have this in 2 colors!
items.body: I love the fit, the comfort and the style of this sweater. It washes beautifully and it always looks good! It is not heavy or bulky and it doesn't itch. Very soft. Read more
items.author: amn81

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Thick warm & well made! Beautiful sweater!
items.body: Absolutely beautiful sweater! Thick, soft, well made. I got two, one in brown & one in wine. The colors are also rich and deep. The wine is a true wine or burgundy, not purplish like so many. This is one of the best sweaters on Amazon! Read more
items.author: Lisa

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice for the price.
items.body: Sweater looks very nice. Figure flattering. Love the color. Being honest, I'm not going to be keeping it because I can tell that the material will be easy to catch and pull a run in the sweater. For someone who isn't clumsy such as myself it's a nice fitting, soft material sweater perfect for the fall weather that will surely be coming soon here in New England. Read more
items.author: Bittersweet

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very nice sweater.
items.body: Nice fabric and fit, looks good, washes well. Read more
items.author: CRKB

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great basic sweater
items.body: Quality sweater at reasonable price. true to size, really nice red. I would get this in other colors. it's not a heavy weight piece if you're looking for something for super cold weather. Read more
items.author: Customer R

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect Florida weight sweater
items.body: The color is a nice, bright red. Very Christmas! I love the way the collared neckline fits snuggly but isn't tight. Fabric is of a medium weight, soft and not scratchy at all. I'm 5'5" 125 lbs. and ordered a small. It's just right. Read more
items.author: marilyn

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars Same company, but the fabric was treated different.
items.body: I bought this style of sweater and a large brown, a large blue and medium blue. The large brown and the large blue are little baggy which I like and they’re soft and cozy. The medium blue is a little form fitting like I wanted but it is not cozy nor soft. It feels like they treated it with some extra special starch. You can fill the ribbing in the material. Read more
items.author: Mary

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

If you are between sizes, choose based on how close you like the fit through the waist and hips, then adjust with your usual layering choices.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress V Neck Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: One Size.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Nutmeg, Grass Green, Red Heart, Grey Blue, Bright Orange, Army Green, Grey Orange Color Block, Black, Coffee, Orange, Apricot Black Stripe, Rose Red, Green Stripe, Plum. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
